est/16_bit_binary.pgm\n```\n\n``` python\nPython 3.4.0 (default, Mar 25 2014, 11:07:05)\n[GCC 4.2.1 Compatible Apple LLVM 5.1 (clang-503.0.38)] on darwin\n>>> import PIL\n>>> PIL.VERSION\n'1.1.7'\n>>> PIL.PILLOW_VERSION\n'2.4.0'\n>>> image = PIL.Image.open('16_bit_binary.pgm')\n>>> image\n<PIL.PpmImagePlugin.PpmImageFile image mode=L size=32x16 at 0x105C76A58>\n>>> len(image.getdata())\n512\n>>> image.save('foo.pgm')\n```\n\n```\n$ identify foo.pgm\nfoo.pgm PGM 32x16 32x16+0+0 8-bit Grayscale Gray 525B 0.000u 0:00.000\n```\n\n``` diff\n--- 16_bit_binary.pgm   2014-04-05 09:13:36.000000000 -0700\n+++ foo.pgm 2014-04-05 09:17:49.000000000 -0700\n@@ -1,5 +1,4 @@\n P5\n-# Here is some 16-bit data.\n 32 16\n-65535\n-L�L�I�J�M�H�J�H�G�L�E�F�H�C�C�D�E�G�M�PR;V�]p]pW�Y�U�G�=6:{$�uL�L�I�J�M�I�J�H�G�M�E�G�H�C�C�C�E�G�M�PR;V�]p]pW�Y�U�G�=6;b$�uM�J�I�I�K�F�G�F�F�H�C�C�F�D�C�F�F�D�K�PSQV�\\H\\HY�X�SQG�=64a\"�I�H�I�F�I�I�C�@�D�E�B�@�E�C�@E�G�B�G�PTiV�Y�[\"[\"W�Q'F�<K-\"�E�H�F�F�H�F�G�C�C�F�E�B�C�B�B�E�B�F�L�SQV�V�Y�[\"X�U�PB�9�0>#�uF�H�D�?G�F�E�D�E�E�F�E�@�C�D�C�D�H�M�R;V�V�[\"X�X�TiSQA�3�-�$�F�F�F�E�G�F�C�F�G�E�E�D�D�C�D�C�F�OR;V�X�W�V�V�V�SQPA�5:-�!��G�G�F�F�E�F�F�D�E�D�E�B�B�C�C�I�K�R;U�V�W�W�U�V�SQOF�A�6�+�\"�E�F�E�A�F�E�F�E�C�F�E�D�A�@�E�M�M�U�V�SQV�SQR;R;R;K�H�@4a,K ��D�F�G�D�G�F�F�I�I�H�C�F�D�E�H�K�Q'U�SQTiU�R;SQM�Q'K�E�>#60>(��E�F�E�E�E�E�G�H�I�G�C�E�A�E�H�OR;U�OTiSQQ'Q'L�K�L�F�@6/p)C\"3F�D�A�F�F�E�G�G�I�F�G�E�C�D�G�OV�W�SQOSQQ'PM�J�K�E�@�:{.�(�D�A�B�F�I�H�G�G�I�E�F�G�F�I�L�R;SQU�W�R;Q'OM�H�K�K�F�@�9�.�$>�D�D�F�D�F�I�H�F�G�I�F�E�G�L�Q'SQSQU�SQTiK�K�K�J�K�K�H�@�9�-� 8�F�I�H�F�G�G�H�G�H�I�I�I�K�R;U�X�W�U�TiPJ�J�G�H�M�M�J�C�7�-\"3�F�H�G�H�H�H�J�I�I�I�J�OQ'TiTiW�W�TiSQM�J�H�E�H�K�OM�D�9�/p#�P5\n+255\n+L�L�I�J�M�H�J�H�G�L�E�F�H�C�C�D�E�G�M�PR;V�]p]pW�Y�U�G�=6:{$�uL�L�I�J�M�I�J�H�G�M�E�G�H�C�C�C�E�G�M�PR;V�]p]pW�Y�U�G�=6;b$�uM�J�I�I�K�F�G�F�F�H�C�C�F�D�C�F�F�D�K�PSQV�\\H\\HY�X�SQG�=64a\"�I�H�I�F�I�I�C�@�D�E�B�@�E�C�@E�G�B�G�PTiV�Y�[\"[\"W�Q'F�<K-\"�E�H�F�F�H�F�G�C�C�F�E�B�C�B�B